RESIDUES, *H* FOR HEAVY-CHAIN RESIDUES.  THE NUMBERING
SYSTEM USED IN THIS ENTRY IS SEQUENTIAL, FROM 1 - 107 FOR
THE LIGHT CHAIN AND FROM 201 - 316 FOR THE HEAVY CHAIN.
PRO L 95 IS TRANS IN THIS DELETION MUTANT.
